videos.description: Cameron McGriff muscles his way for the lay-in plus the foul.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State's McGriff uses his strength to complete the  layup.

videos.description: West Virginia comes up with the steal and then Elijah Macon finishes with the strong dunk.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense for West Virginia

videos.description: Davon Dillard with the long pass to Jeffrey Carroll who gets the layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Long inbounds play leads to lay-in plus the foul for Oklahoma State

videos.description: Davon Dillard splits the defenders, takes off from near the foul line and slams it in for Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Dillard with an epic dunk

videos.description: Lamont West makes the 3-pointer plus the foul to give West Virginia the lead.
videos.headline: West Virginia's West answers back with a 4-point play

videos.description: Bob Huggins throws himself down to the floor after what he thinks is a bad call and receives a technical foul.
videos.headline: Bob Huggins throws himself to the floor

videos.description: Phil Forte III explains how Oklahoma State pulled out a win over West Virginia.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Phil Forte III talk about the keys to the victory over West Virginia
